Crystalbow! (900m since it's really good, grab one at shops) Dragon Claws (Well, Literally but atleast it has a wolf in it) *Operate vesta longsword and it will heal players nearby with 20hp but sacrificing your movement *Operate Ancient Staff to cast multi suicidal ice burst and freeze+damage nearby players for 20hp sacrificing movement (noble eh?) *Stable Source, Remember your server can be your best friend or your worst enemy, so treat it nice! *FUCKING IPBAN!!!!! YAAAAAY!!!! ::ipban *MAGIC SHORTBOW SPECIALL *And much more!

and other shit. Just find more in command.java

To run: Go to 'bin' folder and click 'run' if you face an error right click 'edit' and change the java version to yours.

[size=13pt]NOTE! If you get 'system cannot find path specified etc.....' Alot of people have been asking me for help and it's really easy to fix. Just right click 'runserver' batch file and click 'edit' A notepad will pop-up. Change the 'jre1.6.0_01' to your 'jre1.x.x_.x.x' version. How to Know what version you have? Follow this path map; 'My Computer' -> 'Program Files' -> 'Java' folder -> Look at the folder with the title 'jre1.x.x_.x.x' The x's represent your digit version. Hopefully this will solve frequent FaQs. Enjoy :) [/size]
